      <li><strong>Multiple trips</strong> to Italy across all major regions &mdash; from the Alps to Sicily</li>
      <li><strong>40+ countries</strong> traveled &mdash; but Italy is always the first love</li>
      <li>Navigated Italy's <strong>train system extensively</strong> &mdash; Trenitalia, Italo, and regional lines</li>
      <li>Deep knowledge of <strong>Italian cuisine</strong> &mdash; from Neapolitan pizza to Bolognese ragu to Sicilian street food</li>
      <li>Explored regions most tourists skip &mdash; <strong>Puglia, Basilicata, Umbria, Le Marche</strong></li>
      <li>Real experience with <strong>budget to luxury travel</strong> &mdash; agriturismi, boutique hotels, and everything in between</li>
